  "body": "Issue as a thread for discussion. ..\r\n\r\n\r\nI understand that since transaction fees on ethereum tend to go so high, eth is not usable to buy a pizza over a traditional ethereum transactinons.\r\n\r\nI do not understand why transaction fees needs to be burned.\r\nIf a cap to transactions needs to be applied, why not attribute over gas price to:\r\nThe eth fund to build scools & houses for the poorests. maybe a lot less of poeple will die if some eth gets converted into food, instead of getting burned.\r\n\r\nburn transaction fees? me: no\r\ninvest transaction fees? me: hmm\r\n\r\n",
