    "body": "Sadly, I am not able to create a concrete EIP. I just want to address EIP1559 in regards of simply burning transaction fees, channeling the fees higher than a certain threshold to a fund that helps prevent starvation instead. How to manage such a fund without abuse is indeed a big task. I hope some people get the idea, and add a feature to EIP1559, or create a new EIP that modifies this one, to prevent simply burning assets.",
